title: New Unpatched 0 Days In Microsoft Exchange
description:
In this video I discuss several 0 day vulnerabilities in Microsoft exchange that were reported to Microsoft back in September by Zero Day Initiative and how Microsoft has decided to not issue immediate fixes for these for 2 months.
